summary: ON OT ABOUT OCTOBER 6TH OF 2019, VEHICLE(WHITE 2019 SUBARU ASCENT TOURING) WAS PARKED IN THE GARAGE AND HAD BEEN DRIVEN THE DAY PRIOR. IT  FAILED TO START PRIOR TO A CRITICAL PEDIATRIC SPECIALTY APPOINTMENT. SUBARU SENT A MECHANIC TO JUMPSTART THE CAR AND THE ENGINE TURNED OVER. THE APT WAS MISSED DUE TO THE DELAY. ON OR ABOUT MID-MAY OF 2020 THE VEHICLE FAILED TO START AFTER BEING PARKED IN THE GARAGE. ATTEMPTS TO CHARGE THE BATTERY DID NOT WORK. SUBARU ROADSIDE ASSISTANCE RETURNED AGAIN AND JUMP STARTED THE CAR. IT WAS LEFT TO RUN FOR OVER AN HOUR. THE FOLLOWING DAY IT WOULD NOT START AGAIN.  *TR
